

##--- Lines below are ignored
##--- Only options copied to the first line are considered
## Some possible options:

# To check the GC functioning in the terminal (longer, only to check) e.g.
-XX:+PrintGC

# Shows the jvm version and continues
-showversion

# Various alternative Garbage Collectors, choose one only
-XX:+UseG1GC
-XX:+UseParallelGC
-XX:+UseParallelOldGC
-XX:+UseSerialGC
-XX:+UseConcMarkSweepGC

# Examples
# G1 Garbage Collector and print messages in the terminal:
-XX:+UseG1GC -XX:+PrintGC

# Parallel old Garbage Collector
-XX:+UseParallelOldGC

